<template><view class="page"><view class="title">订阅服务</view><AppCard v-for="x in plans" :key="x.id" :title="x.name"><view>月费 ¥{{x.monthlyPrice}} / 年费 ¥{{x.yearlyPrice}}</view><button class="btn" @click="buy(x.id)">购买</button></AppCard></view></template><script setup lang="ts">import{ref}from'vue';import{onShow}from'@dcloudio/uni-app';import AppCard from'@/components/AppCard.vue';import{qingxierApi}from'@/services/api';const plans=ref<any[]>([]);onShow(async()=>plans.value=await qingxierApi.plans());async function buy(planId:string){const o=await qingxierApi.createOrder({planId,billingCycle:'month'});uni.showToast({title:`订单 ${o.orderNo} 已创建`})}</script>
